ft| {{fbwu|17|CUB}}\n|align=center| {{sort|14|[[2020 CONCACAF Women's U-17 Championship qualifying stage#Teams|14th ranked]] entrant}}\n|align=center|\n|align=center|\n|align=center| 0\n|-\n|align=left| {{fbwu|17|GRN}}\n|align=center| {{sort|15|[[2020 CONCACAF Women's U-17 Championship qualifying stage#Teams|15th ranked]] entrant}}\n|align=center|\n|align=center|\n|align=center| 0\n|-\n|align=left| {{fbwu|17|NCA}}\n|align=center| {{sort|16|[[2020 CONCACAF Women's U-17 Championship qualifying stage#Teams|16th ranked]] entrant}}\n|align=center|\n|align=center|\n|align=center| 0\n|-\n|align=center rowspan=4| Knockout stage\n|align=left| {{fbwu|17|HON}}\n|align=center| {{sort|A|[[2020 CONCACAF Women's U-17 Championship qualifying stage#Group A|Qualifying Group A]] winner}}\n|align=center|\n|align=center|\n|align=center| 0\n|-\n|align=left| {{fbwu|17|CAY}}\n|align=center| {{sort|B|[[2020 CONCACAF Women's U-17 Championship qualifying stage#Group B|Qualifying Group B]] winner}}\n|align=center|\n|align=center|\n|align=center| 0\n|-\n|align=left| {{fbwu|17|BLZ}}\n|align=center| {{sort|C|[[2020 CONCACAF Women's U-17 Championship qualifying stage#Group C|Qualifying Group C]] winner}}\n|align=center|\n|align=center|\n|align=center| 0\n|-\n|align=left| {{fbwu|17|GUY}}\n|align=center| {{sort|D|[[2020 CONCACAF Women's U-17 Championship qualifying stage#Group D|Qualifying Group D]] winner}}\n|align=center|\n|align=center|\n|align=center| 0\n|}\n\n==Venues==\n*[[Mexican Football Federation]] Headquarters, [[Toluca]]\n\n==Draw==\nThe draw for the group stage took place on 9 May 2019, 11:00 [[Eastern Time Zone|EDT]] ([[UTC\u221204:00|UTC\u22124]]), at the CONCACAF Headquarters in [[Miami]]. The 16 teams which entered the group stage were drawn into four groups of four teams.<ref name=\"draw\"/> Based on the CONCACAF Women's Under-17 Ranking, the 16 teams were distributed into four pots, with teams in Pot 1 assigned to each group prior to the draw, as follows:<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.concacaf.com/en/under-17s-women/video/official-draw-2020-concacaf-women-s-under-17-championship|title=Official draw \u2013 2020 CONCACAF Women's Under-17 Championship|publisher=CONCACAF.com}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Pot 1\n!Pot 2\n!Pot 3\n!Pot 4\n|-\n|valign=top|{{plainlist|\n*{{fbwu|17|MEX}} (E1)\n*{{fbwu|17|CAN}} (F1)\n*{{fbwu|17|USA}} (G1)\n*{{fbwu|17|HAI}} (H1)\n}}\n|valign=top|{{plainlist|\n*{{fbwu|17|CRC}}\n*{{fbwu|17|JAM}}\n*{{fbwu|17|TRI}}\n*{{fbwu|17|GUA}}\n}}\n|valign=top|{{plainlist|\n*{{fbwu|17|PUR}}\n*{{fbwu|17|BER}}\n*{{fbwu|17|SLV}}\n*{{fbwu|17|PAN}}\n}}\n|valign=top|{{plainlist|\n*{{fbwu|17|DOM}}\n*{{fbwu|17|CUB}}\n*{{fbwu|17|GRN}}\n*{{fbwu|17|NCA}}\n}}\n|}\n\n==Squads==\n{{Details|2020 CONCACAF Women's U-17 Championship squads}}\n\nPlayers born on or after 1 January 2003 are eligible to compete. Each team must register a squad of 20 players, two of whom must be goalkeepers.<ref name=\"regulations\">{{cite web|url=https://res.cloudinary.com/concacaf-production/image/upload/v1581353741/concacaf-prod/assets/Concacaf_Women_s_Under-17_Championship_-_Regulations_ENG.pdf|title=2020 CONCACAF Women's U-17 Championship Regulations|publisher=CONCACAF}}</ref>\n\n==Group stage==\nThe top three teams in each group will advance to the round of 16, where they are joined by the four teams advancing from the [[2020 CONCACAF Women's U-17 Championship qualifying stage|qualifying stage]].\n{{anchor|Tiebreakers}}\n;Tiebreakers\nThe ranking of teams in each group is determined as follows (Regulations Article 12.8):<ref name=\"regulations\"/>\n#[[Points (association football)|Points]] obtained in all group matches (three points for a win, one for a draw, zero for a loss);\n#[[Goal difference]] in all group matches;\n#Number of goals scored in all group matches;\n#Points obtained in the matches played between the teams in question;\n#Goal difference in the matches played between the teams in question;\n#Number of goals scored in the matches played between the teams in question;\n#Fair play points in all group matches (only one deduction could be applied to a player in a single match):\n#*Yellow card: \u22121 points;\n#*Indirect red card (second yellow card): \u22123 points;\n#*Direct red card: \u22124 points;\n#*Yellow card and direct red card: \u22125 points;\n#Drawing of lots.\n\nAll times are local, [[Central Time Zone|CDT]] ([[UTC\u221205:00|UTC\u22125]]).<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gallery.mailchimp.com/78d3589fb61466b549ff752e5/files/32736f24-e628-4894-a6cb-a3c6f3f05e50/CWU17C_2020_Schedule_Announcement.pdf|title=2020 Match Schedule|publisher=CONCACAF}}</ref>\n\n===Group E===\n{{#invoke:Sports table|main|style=WDL\n\n|source=[https://www.concacaf.com/en/under-17s-women/schedule-results#tab_team=standings CONCACAF]\n|name_MEX={{fbwu|17|MEX}}\n|name_TRI={{fbwu|17|TRI}}\n|name_BER={{fbwu|17|BER}}\n|name_DOM={{fbwu|17|DOM}}\n\n<!--UPDATE standings below (including date)-->\n|update=future |start_date=TBD\n|win_MEX=0 |draw_MEX=0 |loss_MEX=0 |gf_MEX=0 |ga_MEX=0 |status_MEX=H\n|win_TRI=0 |draw_TRI=0 |loss_TRI=0 |gf_TRI=0 |ga_TRI=0 |status_TRI=\n|win_BER=0 |draw_BER=0 |loss_BER=0 |gf_BER=0 |ga_BER=0 |status_BER=\n|win_DOM=0 |draw_DOM=0 |loss_DOM=0 |gf_DOM=0 |ga_DOM=0 |status_DOM=\n\n<!--UPDATE positions below (check tiebreakers)-->\n|team1=MEX |team2=TRI |team3=BER |team4=DOM\n|class_rules=[[#Tiebreakers|Group stage tiebreakers]]\n\n|res_col_header=Q\n|result1=KO |result2=KO |result3=KO\n|col_KO=green1 |text_KO=[[#Knockout stage|Knockout stage]]\n}}\n\n{{Football box\n|date       = <!--{{Start date|2020|||df=y}}-->TBD\n|time       =\n|team1      = {{fbwu-rt|17|TRI}}\n|score      = Match 1\n|team2      = {{fbwu|17|BER}}\n|goals1     =\n|goals2     =\n|stadium    =\n|attendance =\n|referee    =\n|report     = https://www.concacaf.com/en/under-17s-women/game-detail/518670\n}}\n{{Football box\n|date       = <!--{{Start date|2020|||df=y}}-->TBD\n|time       =\n|team1      = {{fbwu-rt|17|MEX}}\n|score      = Match 3\n|team