u/news/562853/zorko-to-lead-in-2020|title=Zorko to lead in 2020|first=Josie|last=Fielding|publisher=[[Telstra Media]]|work=[[Brisbane Lions]]|date=13 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{AFL Car}}\n| [[David Teague (footballer)|David Teague]]\n| [[Patrick Cripps]]<br/>[[Sam Docherty]]\n| \n| [[Ed Curnow]], [[Liam Jones]], [[Marc Murphy]], [[Sam Walsh (footballer)|Sam Walsh]], [[Jacob Weitering]]\n|<ref>{{cite web |title=Three new additions to AFL leadership group |url=https://www.carltonfc.com.au/news/564199/three-new-additions-to-afl-leadership-group |work=[[Carlton Football Club|Carlton]] |publisher=[[Telstra Media]] |date=17 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{AFL Col}}\n| [[Nathan Buckley]]\n| [[Scott Pendlebury]]\n| [[Taylor Adams]], [[Steele Sidebottom]], [[Jeremy Howe]]\n| [[Brodie Grundy]], [[Jordan Roughead]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.collingwoodfc.com.au/news/571776/pendlebury-to-lead-pies-for-a-seventh-season|title=Pendlebury to lead Pies for a seventh season|publisher=[[Telstra Media]]|work=[[Collingwood Football Club|Collingwood]]|date=4 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{AFL Ess}}\n| [[John Worsfold]]\n| [[Dyson Heppell]]\n| \n| [[Michael Hurley (footballer)|Michael Hurley]], [[Dylan Shiel]], [[Devon Smith (footballer)|Devon Smith]], [[David Zaharakis]]\n|<ref>{{cite web |title=2020 leadership group named |url=https://www.essendonfc.com.au/news/559710/2020-leadership-group-named |website=[[Essendon Football Club|Essendon]] |publisher=[[Telstra Media]] |date=4 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{AFL Fre}}\n| [[Justin Longmuir]]\n| [[Nat Fyfe]]\n| \n| [[Reece Conca]], [[Joel Hamling]], [[David Mundy]], [[Alex Pearce (Australian footballer)|Alex Pearce]], [[Michael Walters]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fremantlefc.com.au/news/568658/fremantle-announce-2020-leadership-group|title=Fremantle announce 2020 leadership group|publisher=[[Telstra Media]]|work=[[Fremantle Football Club|Fremantle]]|date=26 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{AFL Gee}}\n| [[Chris Scott (Australia